# Peer-to-Peer Rental Application Documentation

Welcome to the documentation for the Peer-to-Peer Rental Application. This documentation will guide you through the various features and functionalities of the application. The Peer-to-Peer Rental Application allows users to list products for renting, send rental requests, manage listings, and handle payments. Users can sign up or log in using Google OAuth for a seamless authentication experience.

